#String tooltip
Chopper
Chop down trees using axe from your inventory, with uprooting stumps using shovel from your inventory. You can uproot stumps or cut down bushes, also ignore growing trees. Auto-refilling water from nearby container is also possible if you have water barrel (or cistern) in area that is spec "water_refiller". You can also eat food from inventory when hunger is low